metadata.name: DISTANCE
metadata.description:
Have you ever been able to see a feeling? Love, envy, hope?

Would each feeling look different depending on the person? What would loneliness look like?

Through my art I try to put out my inner ocean, this wild and sometimes stormy sea I have inside.

Sometimes I come up with pieces like these. I feel them, I know them. And now I see them. So do you
